%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98temporary%E2%80%99%20provision%2C%20the%20country%20has%20been%20weakened%20while%20those%20powers%20who%20termed%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20accession%20with%20India%20as%20%E2%80%98temporary%E2%80%99%20have%20got%20strengthened.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlleging%20that%20she%20was%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%20on%20Monday%2C%20Mehbooba%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20illegal%20decision%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20the%20parliament%20(on%20August%205%2C%202019)%20and%20the%20legal%20approval%20granted%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20no%20less%20than%20a%20death%20punishment%20for%20the%20idea%20of%20India.%20But%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20fight%20peacefully%20for%20our%20rights%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehbooba%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%20was%20among%20three%20former%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20who%20were%20taken%20into%20preventive%20custody%20in%20August%202019%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20bifurcate%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20downgrade%20it%20to%20union%20territory%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%2C%20the%20PDP%20has%20also%20suspended%20all%20political%20activities%20for%20a%20week%20%E2%80%9Cin%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fin-jammu-and-kashmir-all-eyes-are-on-the-supreme-court-today%5C%22%3EIn%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Verdict%2C%20the%20SC%20Has%20Done%20What%20Many%20Locals%20Had%20Feared%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%20also%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%20on%20Monday%20morning%20ahead%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20live%20broadcast%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Omar%20said%