0Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Tribeni.%20The%20event%20is%20sometimes%20spelt%20%E2%80%98Kumbho%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20expected%20to%20arrive%20at%2011.15%20am%20and%20leave%20around%201.30-2%20pm%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manas%20Bhattacharya%2C%20the%20main%20organiser%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EGita%3C%2Fem%3E%20recital%20event%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20serves%20as%20the%20state%20secretary%20of%20the%20little-known%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Sanskrit%20Parishad%2C%20which%20is%20organising%20the%20event%20in%20association%20with%20Sanatan%20Sanskriti%20Sansad%2C%20an%20organisation%20of%20monks%20formed%20last%20year%2C%20and%20Matilal%20Bharat%20Tirtha%20Seva%20Mission%2C%20an%20NGO%20engaged%20in%20social%20work%20in%20the%20education%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20state%20unit%20president%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%2C%20said%20that%20the%20PM%20has%20given%20a%20%E2%80%9Cverbal%20assurance%E2%80%9D%20but%20any%20written%20communication%20was%20yet%20to%20come.%20In%20November%2C%20Majumdar%20had%20taken%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20event%2C%20including%20Bhattacharya%20and%20monks%2C%20to%20PM%20Modi%20to%20invite%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESadanand%20Saraswati%2C%20the%20Sankaracharya%20of%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Dwaraka%20Sharda%20Peetham%2C%20and%20Bengal%20governor%20C.V.%20Ananda%20Bose%20have%20consented%20to%20be%20present%2C%20Bhattacharya%20said.%20Chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20their%20invitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20praise%20and%20a%20dubious%20history%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELast%20year%2C%20PM%20Modi%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1902487