22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstability%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoffs-sweeping-the-us-these-are-the-companies-making-cuts-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelentless%20upheaval%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20past%20several%20years%20have%20heightened%20these%20feelings.%20Remote%20work%2C%20Malcolmson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bcan%20make%20everything%20feel%20so%20much%20more%20intense.%26quot%3B%20She%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20much%20harder%20for%20me%20to%20mentally%20let%20go%20of%20any%20stresses%20from%20the%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20turmoil%20of%20the%20past%20few%20years%20has%20made%20workers%20of%20all%20ages%20more%20stressed%3A%20In%20Gallup's%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallup.com%2Fworkplace%2F349484%2Fstate-of-the-global-workplace.aspx%3Fthank-you-report-form%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworkplace%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2052%25%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Canada%20said%20they%20felt%20stressed%20at%20work%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20a%20record%20high.%20In%20the%20UK%2C%20work-related%20stress%2C%20anxiety%2C%20and%20depression%20are%20up%2014%25%20from%202020%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdwfgroup.com%2Fen%2Fnews-and-insights%2Finsights%2F2023%2F1%2Fwork-related-stress-and-mental-health-an-emerging-health-and-safety-crisis%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThis%2520is%2520a%2520rise%2520of%2Crelated%2520stress%252C%2520depression%2520or%2520anxiety.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHealth%20and%20Safety%20Executive%20statistics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20Gen%20Zers%2C%20who%20are%20just%20beginning%20their%20career%20journeys%2C%20are%20having%20an%20especially%20difficult%20time.%20In%20a%202022%20survey%20by%20the%20meditation%20app%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finfo.calm.com%2Frs%2F541-LYF-023%2Fimages%2FCalm-Business-2023-Workplace-Mental-Health-Trends-Report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalm%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2058%2