ng%20your%20hands.%20I%20know%2C%20you%20rub%20your%20hands%20when%20you%20are%20nervous.'%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETriptii%20Dimri%20also%20asked%C2%A0about%20the%20%26quot%3Bsuper%26quot%3B%20viral%20video%20of%20her%20looking%20at%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%C2%A0during%20a%20conversation%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAVGBHF-3BJs%5C%22%3EInstant%20Bollywood%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20actress%20said%20that%20she%20was%20too%20nervous%20to%C2%A0realise%20what%20was%20she%20doing%20at%20that%20moment.%20Triptii%20said%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Breally%20nervous%20because%20it%20was%20my%20theatrical%20release%20after%205%20years.%26quot%3B%C2%A0She%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20I%20was%20really%20nervous.%20And%20specially%2C%20when%20you%20are%20standing%20with%20people%20like%20Ranbir%2C%20you%20are%20bound%20to%20get%20nervous%2C%20right%3F%20And%20I%20think%20he%20was%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20me%2C%20talking%20to%20somebody%20and%20you%20don't%20even%20realise%20in%20that%20moment%2C%20where%20you%20are%20looking%2C%20what%20you%20are%20looking%20at.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20the%20video%20from%20the%20%3Ci%3EAnimal%20%3C%2Fi%3Escreening%20we%20are%20talking%20about%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EShe%20can't%20take%20her%20eyes%20off%20from%20Him..%20We%20get%20it%20tripti%3F%3F%3F%3F%E2%9D%A4%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FssiXfToYtW%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FssiXfToYtW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20%E2%9C%A8%20(%40lehrein_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flehrein_%2Fstatus%2F1732400046719832324%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETriptii%20Dimri%2C%20recently%2C%20also%20opened%20up%20about%20shooting%20the%20intimate%20scene%20with%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20in%20%3Ci%3EAnimal%3C%2Fi%3E.%