0man%20lost%20more%20than%20150%20pounds%20after%20retiring%20by%20walking%20and%20tracking%20macros.%20Here's%20his%20routine.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Retiree%20Ken%20Jones%20standing%20in%20his%20kitchen%20in%20workout%20clothes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65720f0358e7c0c29a2ab6f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKen%20Jones%20lost%20more%20than%20150%20pounds%20since%20his%20retirement%20in%202015%20through%20a%20combination%20of%20walking%20and%20tracking%20his%20macros.%20He%20also%20achieved%20his%20lifetime%20goal%20of%20winning%20a%20bodybuilding%20competion%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ken%20Jones%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%2059-year-old%20man%20lost%20more%20than%20150%20pounds%20by%20walking%20and%20tracking%20his%20macronutrients.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20he%20had%20planned%20to%20get%20back%20in%20shape%20after%20gradually%20gaining%20weight%20over%20the%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20started%20competing%20in%20bodybuilding%20show%2C%20and%20even%20won%20a%20contest%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20that%20Texas%20resident%20Ken%20Jones%20retired%2C%20he%20went%20for%20a%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20first%20small%20step%20of%20what%20would%20become%20a%20more%20than%20eight-year%20fitness%20journey%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20total%20of%20more%20than%20150%20pounds%20of%20weight%20loss%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20says%20I'm%20half%20the%20person%20I%20used%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20coordinated%20by%20the%20health%20tracking%20app%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D97c0b57ecf5515b8fe5fe3b88081a1f10e6edc12f140c30663e4ecfa421df793%26postID%3D657203f333f7fba9f6473dff%26postSlug%3Dtracking-macros-walking-diet-lost-over-hundred-pounds-2023-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.myfitnesspal.com%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMyFitnessPal%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20at%20age%2059%2C%20Jones%20has%20also%20achieved%20his%20lifelong%20goal%20of%20winning%20a%20bodybuilding%20competition%2C%20and%20even%20hopes%20to%20go%20pro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20the%20change%20happened%20outside%20the%20gym%2C%20Jones%20said.%20Simple%20healthy%20habits%20like%20regular%20walking%20and%20tracking%20his%20macronutrients%2C%20without%20keeping%20a%20strict%20diet%2C%20were%20key%20to%20his%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20lost%2080%20pounds%20just%20by%20walking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Jones%20neared%20his%20retirement%20date%20in%202015%2C%20he%20knew%20it%20was%20time%20for%20a%20change.%20He%20said%20that%20while%20he%20was%20athletic%20as%20a%20young%20man%2C%20a%20combination%20of%20shift%20work%20at%20the%20Dow%20Chemical%20plant%2C%20stress%2C%20and%20a%20busy%20schedule%20got%20in%20the%20way%2C%20causing%20him%20to%20gradually%20gain%20weight%20and%20lose%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20he%20had%20planned%20for%20years%20to%20make%20a%20post-retirement%20transformation%2C%20but%20was%20hesitant%20about%20jumping%20back%20into%20intensive%20workouts.%20So%20he%20opted%20to%20start%20his%20fitness%20journey%20with%20simple%20walks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20day%20after%20I%20retired%2C%20I%20just%20started%20walking%20because%20I%20was%20in%20no%20kind%20of%20shape%20to%20walk%20into%20a%20gym.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20Jones%20had%20dropped%20about%2080%20pounds%20by%20walking%20regularly%20and%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20what%20he%20ate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%2C%20and%20experts%2C%20suggest%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-five-hundred-extra-steps-per-day-live-longer-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewalking%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20improve%20your%20health%20and%20fitness%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20as%20a%20beginner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20build%20muscle%2C%20he%20started%20tracking%20macros%20like%20protein%20and%20carbs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Jones%20continued%20to%20progress%20in%20his%20fitness%20journey%2C%20he%20started%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20nutrition%20by%20talking%20to%20other%20athletes%2C%20in%20pursuit%20of%20his%20eventual%20goal%20of%20signing%20up%20for%20a%20bodybuilding%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20hired%20a%20trainer%2C%20who%20began%20helping%20him%20fine-tune%20his%20nutrition%20using%20the%20app%20MyFitnessPal.%20The%20main%20change%20to%20his%20eating%20habits%20was%20that%20he%20began%20carefully%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalories-macros-protein-fat-weight-loss-expert-advice-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etracking%20macronutrients%20%E2%80%94%20carbs%2C%20fat%2C%20and%20protein%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20to%20hit%20the%20daily%20targets%20his%20trainer%20set%20for%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20instructions%20are%2C%20'you%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20eat%20what%20you%20want%2C%20but%20don't%20you%20go%20below%2C%20and%20don't%20you%20go%20over%20the%20numbers%20I%20give%20you%2C'%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said%20of%20his%20trainer's%20advice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20focusing%20on%20macro%20numbers%2C%20Jones%20said%20he%20was%20able%20to%20eat%20a%20wider%20variety%20of%20foods%2C%20while%20still%20having%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20stay%20on%20track%20toward%20his%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20said%20tracking%20his%20macros%20is%20now%20a%20part%20of%20his%20daily%20routine.%20Every%20morning%2C%20he%20weighs%20in%2C%20then%20sits%20down%20with%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%20to%20enter%20his%20weight%20in%20a%20spreadsheet%20and%20then%20log%20all%20his%20upcoming%20meals%20for%20the%20day%20in%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20goes%20in%20my%20mouth%20unless%20it%20goes%20in%20MyFitnessPal%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20track%20your%20macros.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%20his%20daily%20diet%20involves%20ground%20turkey%2C%20tilapia%2C%20oatmeal%2C%20and%20peanut%20butter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Jones%20said%20he%20eats%20about%202%2C100%20calories%20a%20day%20on%20average%20(which%20will%20gradually%20decrease%20leading%20up%20to%20competition).%20That%20breaks%20down%20into%20about%20215%20grams%20of%20protein%2C%20165%20grams%20of%20carbs%2C%20and%2052%20grams%20of%20fat%20for%20five%20days%20of%20the%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20typical%20day%20of%20eating%20includes%20oatmeal%20for%20breakfast%20to%20provide%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fpreworkout-foods-fuel-weight-lifting-high-intensity-workouts-sports-dietitian%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epre-workout%20carbs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20followed%20by%20some%20combination%20of%20lean%20ground%20turkey%20or%20tilapia%20with%20rice%20for%20lunch%20and%20dinner.%20Go-to%20foods%20like%20yogurt%20and%20powdered%20peanut%20butter%20help%20round%20in%20his%20protein%20for%20the%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwice%20a%20week%2C%20Jones%20enjoys%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcarb-cycling-helped-boost-workouts-but-hard-to-adjust-to-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehigher-carb%20day%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20his%20trainer%2C%20which%20he%20takes%20advantage%20of%20to%20enjoy%20Sunday%20pancakes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20that%2C%20he%20doesn't%20vary%20much%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20track%20his%20meals%20using%20the%20copy-and-paste%20feature%20of%20the%20app.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20pretty%20simple%20man%2C%20I%20like%20consistency%2C%20so%20I%20pretty%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcan-you-eat-same-thing-every-day-and-be-healthy-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eeat%20the%20same%20things%20every%20day%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20careful%20diet%2C%20Jones%20said%20he%20works%20out%20six%20days%20a%20week%20for%20about%20an%20hour%20to%2090%20minutes%20a%20day%2C%20including%2020%20minutes%20of%20cardio%20on%20the%20stair-stepper%20machine.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20the%20workouts%20are%20secondary%20to%20other%20healthy%20habits%20in%20order%20to%20achieve%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20what%20you%20do%20in%20the%20gym%2C%20it's%20what%20you%20do%20when%20you%20walk%20out%20that%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftracking-macros-walking-diet-lost-over-hundred-pounds-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702290901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6572114658e7c0c29a2ab81e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftracking-macros-walking-diet-lost-over-hundred-pounds-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20who%20started%20his%20fitness%20journey%20after%20retiring%20in%202015%20has%20since%20lost%20nearly%20half%20his%20body%20weight%20by%20tracking%20his%20macronutrients%20and%20walking.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22glandsverk%40insider.com%20(Gabby%20Landsverk)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftracking-macros-walking-diet-lost-over-hundred-pounds-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20Hezbollah%20fighters%20among%204%20dead%20in%20Israel%20strikes%20near%20Damascus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702290894000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F