99s%20brutal%20and%20massively%20disproportionate%20retaliation%20to%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20murderous%20rampage%20on%20October%207%20has%20drawn%20much%20condemnation%20but%20little%20action.%20Security%20council%20vacillation%20on%20calling%20for%20a%20cease-fire%20forced%20secretary-general%20Guterres%20to%20invoke%20article%2099%20of%20the%20charter%2C%20which%20requires%20the%20security%20council%20to%20meet%20urgently%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20four%20decades.%20But%20the%20U.S.%20vetoed%20the%20council%E2%80%99s%20resolution%20for%20an%20immediate%20cease-fire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20prosecutors%20of%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20(ICC)%2C%20which%20began%20investigating%20war%20crimes%20and%20settler%20violence%20in%202021%2C%20argue%20that%20both%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20attack%20and%20the%20Israeli%20retaliation%20can%20be%20considered%20genocide%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity.%20But%20the%20ICC%E2%80%99s%20current%20chief%20prosecutor%2C%20Karim%20Khan%2C%20visited%20the%20Rafah%20crossing%20four%20unbearable%20weeks%20into%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza.%20He%20visited%20Israel%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20only%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20He%20is%20yet%20to%20visit%20Gaza.%20Small%20wonder%20Palestinian%20human%20rights%20groups%20refused%20to%20meet%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20560px)%2085vw%2C%20560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08150335%2Fimage560x340cropped.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08150335%2Fimage560x340cropped.jpg%20560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08150335%2Fimage560x340cropped-300x182.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688317%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22340%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMen%20walk%20through%20the%20destroyed%20streets%20of%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20WHO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20while%20violence%20escalates%20with%20even%20more%20sickening%20instances%20of%20brutality%2C%20and%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Palestinians%20from%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20continues%2C%20international%20policymakers%20have%20started%20talking%20about%20%E2%80%98the%20day%20after%E2%80%99.%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20plans%20to%20turn%20most%20of%20north%20Gaza%20into%20a%20military%20buffer%20zone%20after%20his%20war%20cabinet%20decides%20that%20Hamas%20has%20been%20destroyed%2C%20and%20refuses%20to%20check%20settler%20expansion%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Vice-President%20Kamala%20Harris%20have%20opposed%20his%20plan%2C%20but%20agree%20that%20security%20for%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20should%20remain%20with%20Israel%20until%20a%20lasting%20solution%20is%20found.%20But%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20security%20control%20is%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20exacerbated%20by%20Egypt%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20open%20its%20borders%20to%20Gazan%20refugees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20peace%20activist%20Avi%20Shlaim%20has%20repeatedly%20stressed%2C%20successive%20Israeli%20prime%20ministers%20used%20control%20over%20Palestinian%20security%20to%20undermine%20the%201992-1993%20Oslo%20accords%20through%20settlement%20expansion.%20They%20encountered%20little%20resistance%20from%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Europe%20or%20the%20Arab%20countries.%20Writing%20in%202011%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20columnist%20Irfan%20Husain%2C%20whose%20selected%20works%20I%20have%20been%20reading%20over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20commented%20bitterly%20that%20Palestine%E2%80%99s%20Arab%20neighbours%20and%20the%20larger%20comity%20of%20Muslim%20countries%20had%20abandoned%20the%20Palestinians%3B%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20failed%20their%20own%20people%20who%20overwhelmingly%20supported%20the%20Palestinian%20right%20to%20self-determination%20(Irfan%20Husain%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Life%20Lived%20with%20Passion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%202023).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwitnessing-palestine-in-new-york-and-watching-indias-moral-vision-disappear%5C%22%3EWitnessing%20Palestine%20in%20New%20York%20%E2%80%93%20and%20Watching%20India%E2%80%99s%20Moral%20Vision%20Disappear%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20failure%20of%20the%20Oslo%20accords%20and%20the%20fragmentation%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20into%20isolated%20hamlets%20under%20constant%20threat%20from%20settlers%20is%20clear%20indication%20that%20an%20incremental%20process%20will%20not%20work.%20It%20may%20be%20that%20an%20interim%20arrangement%20is%20necessary%20to%20allow%20cooling-off%20before%20political%20negotiations%20for%20a%20lasting%20solution%20begin.%20If%20so%2C%20security%20will%20need%20to%20be%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20an%20international%20peace-keeping%20force.%20The%20Netanyahu%20administration%20will%20be%20extremely%20reluctant%20to%20accept%20such%20a%20force%2C%20but%20the%20US%20has%20sufficient%20power%20to%20pressure%20it%20into%20agreement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20could%20a%20lasting%20solution%20comprise%3F%20Most%20countries%20favour%20a%20two-state%20solution%20based%20on%20the%201967%20borders%2C%20which%20the%20bulk%20of%20policy%20analysts%20suggest%20is%20dead%3B%20some%20peace%20advocates%20suggest%20a%20binational%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPartition%20has%20rarely%20been%20a%20desired%20outcome%2C%20even%20in%20countries%20that%20acceded%20to%20it%2C%20and%20it%20has%20had%20mixed%20results%20as%20the%20least%20bad%20solution%2C%20often%20resulting%20in%20entrenching%20rather%20than%20overcoming%20hostility.%20Given%20that%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20only%20feasible%20solution%2C%20however%2C%20are%20there%20any%20lessons%20on%20how%20to%20minimise%20its%20negative%20outcomes%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98What%20if%E2%80%99%20analyses%20are%20rare%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20but%20Irfan%20found%20that%20one%20plus%20of%20partition%20was%20that%20it%20had%20benefited%20Pakistan%20economically.%20The%20flow%20of%20Muslim%20elites%20from%20India%20brought%20intellectual%20and%20technical%20expertise%20which%20combined%20with%20liberal%20economic%20policies%20to%20develop%20what%20had%20earlier%20been%20underdeveloped%20areas.%20A%20similar%20inflow%20might%20well%20occur%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20territories%20if%20the%20occupation%20ends%2C%20with%20the%20benefit%20of%20stability%20for%20Israel.%20But%20much%20will%20depend%20on%20whether%20Israel%20will%20resume%20employment%20of%20labor%20from%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20whose%20wages%20make%20up%20close%20to%20a%20quarter%20of%20both%20economies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16120732%2Fimage1170x530cropped-5.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16120732%2Fimage1170x530cropped-5.jpg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16120732%2Fimage1170x530cropped-5-300x136.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16120732%2Fimage1170x530cropped-5-1024x464.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685017%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELarge%20areas%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20have%20been%20destroyed%20by%20missile%20strikes.%20Photo%3A%20WHO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20India-Pakistan%20negatives%20are%20more%20numerous.%20Pakistan%20%E2%80%93%20as%20Reginald%20Copeland%20foresaw%20in%20the%201940s%20%E2%80%93%20invested%20ruinous%20amounts%20in%20security%2C%20a%20problem%20that%20might%20not%20occur%20in%20the%20Israeli%20or%20Palestinian%20case%2C%20since%20the%20former%20will%20save%20by%20ending%20the%20occupation%20and%20the%20latter%20will%20most%20likely%20depend%20on%20neighbour%20or%20international%20security%20guarantees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20both%20Pakistan%20and%20India%2C%20Husain%20wrote%2C%20fear%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20other%E2%80%99%20drove%20persecution%20and%20%E2%80%98robbed%20us%20of%20our%20humanity%E2%80%9D.%20The%20two%20could%20not%20settle%20disputes%20that%20were%20counterproductive%20for%20both%2C%20such%20as%20the%20troops-guzzling%2C%20financially%20exorbitant%20and%20ecologically%20damaging%20Siachen%20conflict.%20Had%20pre-partition%20economic%20interchange%2C%20freedom%20of%20movement%20and%20channels%20of%20communication%20been%20kept%20open%20between%20both%20countries%20post-partition%2C%20at%20least%20at%20the%20level%20of%20civil%20society%2C%20the%20two%20polities%20might%20have%20cultivated%20tolerance%2C%20without%20which%20%E2%80%9Ca%20constitution%20and%20all%20the%20trappings%20of%20democracy%20are%20worthless%E2%80%9D%20Husain%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20seems%20odd%20to%20discuss%20a%20long-term%20settlement%20when%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20is%20to%20wrest%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20provide%20humanitarian%20aid.%20But%20even%20if%20this%20horrifically%20brutal%20war%20ends%20soon%2C%20violence%20will%20recur%20as%20long%20as%20the%20occupation%20of%20Palestinian%20territories%20continues.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20all%20agree%20that%20neither%20a%20two-state%20nor%20a%20binational%20state%20agreement%20will%20transpire%20without%20coordinated%20and%20substantive%20international%20pressure%2C%20of%20which%20little%20has%20been%20seen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20reiterated%20his%20support%20for%20a%20two-state%20solution%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20But%20the%20Modi%20administration%20is%20yet%20to%20join%20or%20contribute%20to%20the%20increasing%20number%20of%20countries%20demanding%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20end%20to%20the%20occupation.%20That%20is%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20with%20not%20only%20most%20of%20the%20countries%20of%20%E2%80%98the%20Global%20South%E2%80%99%20but%20also%20the%20countries%20that%20underwent%20colonialism%20and%20oppose%20it%20now.%20Worse%2C%20it%20ignores%20the%20opinion%20of%20millions%20of%20Indian%20citizens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERadha%20Kumar%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20policy%20analyst.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702290629000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03120804%2Fisrael-palestine.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fa-lasting-solution-for-israel-palestine-a-ceasefire-and-an-end-to-occupation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20if%20this%20horrifically%20brutal%20war%20ends%20soon%2C%20violence%20will%20recur%20as%20long%20as%20the%20occupation%20of%20Palestinian%20territories%20continues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fa-lasting-solution-for-israel-palestine-a-ceasefire-and-an-end-to-occupation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rashmika's%20ivory%20saree%20is%20an%20ethnic%20dream%20come%20true%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702290600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105895321%2Cimgsize-42744.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%