a%20lot%20to%20fix%20and%20resolve%20before%20I%20would%20even%20encourage%20anyone%20to%20move%20or%20live%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Texas%20native%20Ty%20Joerger%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20multimedia%20producer%2C%20who%20moved%20to%20Seattle%20in%20July.%20The%20essay%2C%20which%20also%20incorporates%20quotes%20from%20emails%20between%20Joerger%20and%20BI%2C%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20lifelong%20Texan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20born%20in%20Houston%2C%20lived%20in%20San%20Antonio%20as%20a%20child%2C%20and%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20Dallas-Fort%20Worth%20area.%20After%20living%20in%20the%20Lone%20Star%20State%20for%20my%20entire%20life%2C%20I%20moved%20away%20from%20Texas%20in%20July%20%E2%80%94%20all%20the%20way%20to%20Seattle%2C%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20just%20one%20of%20about%2010%20to%2012%20friends%20who%20all%20moved%20from%20Texas%20to%20the%20Pacific%20Northwest%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20Prior%20to%202021%2C%20I%20had%20a%20few%20friends%20who%20moved%20to%20Seattle%2C%20but%20the%20brunt%20of%20my%20friends%20ended%20up%20moving%20in%20late%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20laundry%20list%20of%20reasons%20as%20to%20why%20I%20moved%20away%20from%20Texas.%20A%20consistent%20reason%20among%20me%20and%20my%20friends%20is%20the%20political%20climate%2C%20especially%20with%20all%20of%20us%20being%20members%20of%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20also%20want%20to%20be%20with%20your%20friend%20circle.%20I%20always%20say%20that%20was%20my%20No.%201%20reason%20for%20coming%20up%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20a%20more%20tolerant%20environment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friends%20and%20I%20shared%20a%20pretty%20similar%20sentiment%3A%20That%20we%20didn't%20feel%20safe%20in%20a%20state%20that%20had%20more%20and%20more%20aggressive%20legislation%20targeting%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joerger%20%20smiling%20with%20friends%20at%20a%20Seattle%20Mariners%20game%20in%20Seattle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65723f0558e7c0c29a2ad905%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221065%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoerger%20with%20friends%20at%20a%20Seattle%20Mariners%20baseball%20game.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ty%20Joerger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20gay%20man%2C%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20I%20could%20be%20myself%2C%20and%20always%20felt%20hesitant%20to%20bring%20up%20my%20sexuality%20or%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20have%20a%20boyfriend.%20I%20didn't%20come%20out%20to%20my%20boss%20until%20I%20had%20a%20political%20debate%20with%20him%20and%20had%20to%20make%20a%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20my%20time%20in%20Texas%2C%20I%20was%20a%20little%20more%20open%20about%20it.%20But%20even%20still%2C%20I%20wasn't%20telling%20people%20I%20was%20queer%20or%20parading%20pride%20flags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20I%20didn't%20even%20go%20to%20any%20pride%20parades%20in%20Texas%20because%20I%20was%20scared%20and%20knew%20that%20the%20state%20has%20lax%20gun%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMass%20shootings%20caused%20anxiety%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gun%20policies%20in%20the%20state%20were%20another%20significant%20reason%20for%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20witnessing%20mass%20shooting%20after%20mass%20shooting.%20Some%20of%20these%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fuvalde-victim-parent-dont-look-away-graphic-mass-shooting-images-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUvalde%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsutherland-springs-2-locals-stopped-church-mass-shooter-2017-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESutherland%20Springs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D