y%20of%20Ty%20Joerger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20aspect%20of%20Texas%20that%20I%20don't%20think%20gets%20talked%20about%20enough%20is%20the%20complete%20lack%20of%20public%20transit%20within%20the%20major%20cities.%20While%20Houston%20and%20Dallas%20have%20some%20public%20transit%20with%20METRO%20%26amp%3B%20DART%2C%20they%20don't%20even%20compare%20to%20systems%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Dallas-Fort%20Worth%20metroplex%2C%20you%20pretty%20much%20have%20to%20expect%20a%20more-than-30-minute%20drive%20to%20get%20anywhere%20of%20significance.%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20car%20in%20Texas%2C%20you%20are%20extremely%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Seattle%2C%20I%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20travel%20options.%20The%20accessibility%20of%20getting%20around%20is%20such%20a%20nice%20thing.%20You%20really%20feel%20like%20you%20live%20in%20a%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20think%20I%20made%20the%20right%20decision%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20lived%20in%20Texas%20all%20my%20life%20and%20I%20am%20so%20glad%20I%20moved%20to%20Seattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3El%20think%20it's%20a%20friendlier%20place%20and%20I%20feel%20so%20much%20safer%2C%20and%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20are%20able%20to%20be%20ourselves.%20It's%20a%20little%20more%20expensive%20to%20live%20here%2C%20but%20honestly%20the%20cost%20can%20sometimes%20be%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joerger%20next%20to%20a%20car%20when%20he%20first%20arrived%20in%20Seattle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65723fcf0ec98e92f74d5739%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoerger%20next%20to%20a%20car%20when%20he%20first%20arrived%20in%20Seattle.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ty%20Joerger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20have%20a%20ton%20of%20criticism%20towards%20my%20home%20state%2C%20I%20still%20love%20it.%20I%20do%20miss%20the%20food%20and%20t