%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105900124%2Cimgsize-103658.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fexplained-why-sc-has-recommended-truth-and-reconciliation-commission-for-in-article-370-verdict%2Farticleshow%2F105900092.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Solicitor%20General%20Credits%20PM's%20%26quot%3BIron%20Will%26quot%3B%20After%20Supreme%20Court's%20J%26amp%3BK%20Ruling%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20to%20uphold%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20credited%20the%20development%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Biron%20will%26quot%3B%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20%26quot%3Bbrilliant%20strategy%26quot%3B%20of%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20upheld%20the%20Union%20Government's%20decision%20to%20abrogate%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20gave%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20said%20that%20every%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20Centre%20on%20behalf%20of%20a%20State%20can't%20be%20subject%20to%20a%20legal%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20only%20the%20iron%20will%20of%20our%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modiji%20and%20resolute%20decisiveness%20and%20brilliant%20strategy%20of%20our%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shahji%20that%20made%20this%20historical%20decision%20possible.%20The%20nation%20will%20ever%20remain%20indebted%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tushar%20Mehta%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20had%20the%20good%20fortune%20of%20witnessing%20and%20being%20a%20part%20of%20the%20entire%20process%20which%20exhibited%20their%20exemplary%20resolve%20coupled%20with%20minute%20coordination%20of%20the%20smallest%20details%20and%20flawless%20and%20scientific%20stewardship%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20process%20and%20floor%20management%20inside%20the%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20SG%20Mehta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%20hailed%20the%20five%20judge%20bench%20judgement%20saying%20that%20it%20showed%20concern%20for%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20a%20visible%20concern%20for%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20equality%20of%20every%20resident%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20judicial%20adjudication%20by%20the%20Hon'ble%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20also%20equally%20historical%20and%20rare.%20A%20five%20Judge%20Constitution%20Bench%20decided%20the%20matter%20which%20consisted%20of%20all%20first%20five%20senior-most%20judges%20viz.%20Dr.%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20Hon'ble%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20Justice%20S.K.%20Kaul%2C%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20Justice%20Bhushan%20R.%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant.%20A%20historical%20bench%20presided%20by%20the%20Hon'ble%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20and%20also%20comprising%20of%20three%20future%20Chief%20Justices%20of%20India.%20All%20five%20are%20legendary%20judges%20who%20are%20undisputable%20intellectual%20giants.%20Very%20patient%20hearing%20given%20to%20all%20sides%20for%20more%20than%20three%20weeks.%20And%20today%20comes%20a%20judgment%20which%20will%20go%20down%20in%20the%20history%20of%20this%20great%20country%20exhibiting%20astounding%20scholarship%2C%20concern%20for%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20a%20visible%20concern%20for%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20equality%20of%20every%20resident%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20irrespective%20of%20religion%2C%20sex%2C%20caste%20or%20creed.%20The%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20most%20powerful%20court%20in%20the%20world%2C%20has%20stood%20by%20the%20constitutional%20values%20and%20has%20secured%20to%20all%20the%20residents%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20their%20legitimate%20rights%20which%20they%20were%20deprived%20of%20since%20independence%20while%20taking%20care%20of%20democratic%20election%20also%26quot%3B%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20said%20in%20his%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20getting%20in%20into%20the%20history%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20and%20mentioning%20nations%20first%20home%20minister%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%20Mehta%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHaving%20extensively%20read%20the%20history%20behind%20insertion%20of%20Article%20370%20into%20our%20constitution%2C%20I%20can%20confidently%20say%20that%20the%20soul%20of%20Sardar%20Patel%20will%20be%20fully%20contended%20today%20as%20the%20provision%20which%20he%20could%20not%20prevent%20from%20being%20inserted%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20has%20finally%20gone.%20He%20must%20be%20showering%20his%20blessings%20upon%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah.%20The%20speech%20of%20Shri%20Amit%20Shahji%20in%20Parliament%20is%20as%20historical%20as%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20debates%20and%20will%20go%20down%20in%20the%20history%20as%20one%20of%20the%20few%20statesmanly%20speeches%20while%20shaping%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20India%20in%20more%20than%20one%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20hailed%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20uphold%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20in%20his%20post%20on%20X%20said%20%26quot%3BToday's%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20on%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20is%20historic%20and%20constitutionally%20upholds%20the%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20Parliament%20of%20India%20on%205th%20August%202019%3B%20it%20is%20a%20resounding%20declaration%20of%20hope%2C%20progress%20and%20unity%20for%20our%20sisters%20and%20brothers%20in%20Jammu%2C%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh.%20The%20Court%2C%20in%20its%20profound%20wisdom%2C%20has%20fortified%20the%20very%20essence%20of%20unity%20that%20we%2C%20as%20Indians%2C%20hold%20dear%20and%20cherish%20above%20all%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20further%20assured%20that%20the%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20the%20resilient%20people%20of%20Jammu%2C%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh%20in%20fulfilling%20their%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20assure%20the%20resilient%20people%20of%20Jammu%2C%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh%20that%20our%20commitment%20to%20fulfilling%20your%20dreams%20remains%20unwavering.%20We%20are%20determined%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20fruits%20of%20progress%20not%20only%20reach%20you%20but%20also%20extend%20their%20benefits%20to%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20and%20marginalised%20sections%20of%20our%20society%20who%20suffered%20due%20to%20Article%20370%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20verdict%20today%20is%20not%20just%20a%20legal%20judgment%3B%20it%20is%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%2C%20a%20promise%20of%20a%20brighter%20future%20and%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20collective%20resolve%20to%20build%20a%20stronger%2C%20more%20united%20India.%20%23NayaJammuKashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20the%20central%20government%20announced%20the%20revocation%20of%20the%20special%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20granted%20under%20Article%20370%20and%20split%20the%20region%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%20)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702285500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fc86m6qlo_solicitor-general-tushar-mehta_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsolicitor-general-tushar-mehta-credits-pm-modis-iron-will-after-supreme-court-upholds-abrogation-of-article-370-4653108%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20to%20u