%2Ftop-stories%2Farticle-370-supreme-court-abrogation-of-special-status-of-jammu-and-kashmir-244198%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20not%20every%20decision%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20can%20be%20challenged%3A%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20decision%20taken%20by%20Union%20on%20behalf%20of%20State%20during%20Presidential%20rule%20not%20open%20to%20challenge%E2%80%A6this%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20administration%20of%20state%20to%20a%20standstill.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20coming%20from%20the%20apex%2C%20constitutional%20court%20of%20India%2C%20has%20implications%2C%20especially%20if%20said%20as%20part%20of%20an%20order%20and%20while%20there%20is%20an%20executive%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98strong%E2%80%99%20majority%20in%20place.%20It%20calls%20to%20question%20the%20power%20of%20every%20citizen%2C%20in%20principle%2C%20expecting%20the%20courts%20to%20be%20able%20to%20act%20as%20a%20check%20on%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22As%20Supreme%20Court%20Rules%20on%20Article%20370%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20Here%E2%80%99s%20Why%20History%2C%20Legal%20Context%20Matters%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Farticle-370-understanding-the-history-legal-contexts-and-why-it-matters%5C%22%3EAs%20Supreme%20Court%20Rules%20on%20Article%20370%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20Here%E2%80%99s%20Why%20History%2C%20Legal%20Context%20Matters%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20The%20court%20has%20held%20that%20it%20is%20not%20going%20into%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20parliament%20can%20convert%20a%20state%20into%20a%20union%20territory%2C%20and%20left%20this%20open.%20The%20reorganisation%20of%20Ladakh%20as%20a%20union%20territory%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Farticle-370-supreme-court-abrogation-of-special-status-of-jammu-and-kashmir-244198%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Ewas%20upheld%20as%20Article%203%20allowed%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20state%20to%20be%20made%20as%20UT.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20court%20said%20that%20it%20is%20doing%20so%20because%20the%20solicitor%20general%20has%20promised%20that%20statehood%20will%20be%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20question%20was%20if%20the%20statehood%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20can%20be%20done%20away%20with%2C%20with%20no%20state%20assembly%20being%20in%20place%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20arrogating%20to%20parliament%20the%20powers%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20behalf%20and%20stripping%20down%20its%20status.%20This%20was%20a%20first%20in%20India%20and%20the%20apex%20court%20not%20going%20into%20it%20has%20implications%20on%20future%20attempts%20by%20this%20government%20or%20another%20in%20its%20place%2C%20embarking%20on%20drives%20to%20make%20fundamental%20changes%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20federal%20structure%2C%20of%20which%20states%20are%20the%20central%20building%20blocks.%20Does%20this%20make%20Article%201%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20union%20of%20states%E2%80%9D%2C%20up%20for%20challenge%20too%2C%20or%20render%20it%20an%20%E2%80%9Copen%E2%80%9D%20proposition%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20The%20court%20directed%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20hold%20elections%20%E2%80%9Cby%20September%2030%2C%202024%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20was%20interesting%20as%20it%20effectively%20meant%20directing%20an%20autonomous%20body%20(the%20Election%20Commission)%20which%20is%20meant%20to%20decide%20on%20when%20to%20hold%20polls%20independently.%20The%20call%20for%20elections%20was%20not%20a%20prayer%20in%20any%20of%20the%20petitions.%20In%20effect%2C%20it%20allows%20the%20postponing%20of%20polls%20to%20beyond%20even%20the%20time%20when%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20is%20set%20to%20go%20to%20polls%20in%20a%20general%20election%20by%20spring%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20not%20seen%20assembly%20elections%20in%20nearly%20a%20decade%3B%20the%20last%20time%20polls%20were%20held%20was%20in%20five%20phases%20between%20November-December%202014.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20current%20favourite%20theme%20of%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20simultaneous%20polls%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffull-text-karan-thapar-tarunabh-khaitan-bjp-narendra-modi-hindu-rashtra%5C%22%3EAutocrats%20Have%20Learnt%20To%20Push%20Their%20Agenda%20While%20Retaining%20Paraphernalia%20of%20Democracy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kishen%20Kaul%20in%20his%20epilogue%20has%20mooted%20a%20%E2%80%98truth%20and%20reconciliation%20committee%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20union%20territory%2C%20a%20time-bound%20exercise%20to%20investigate%20and%20report%20on%20the%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20by%20both%20State%20and%20non-state%20actors%20at%20least%20since%20the%201980s%20and%20recommend%20measures%20for%20reconciliation.%20Justice%20Kaul%20mentioned%20the%20South%20African%20commission%20for%20truth%20and%20reconciliation%20as%20a%20model%20and%20said%20it%20should%20be%20done%20to%20heal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fbuzz%2Farticle-370-case-judgment-live-updates-from-supreme-court-on-jammu-kashmir-special-status-25656%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cinter-generational%20trauma%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbefore%20memory%20escapes%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECould%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20look%20upon%20this%20as%20a%20model%20on%20key%20questions%20and%20divides%20which%20are%20wide%20open%20at%20a%20time%20of%20extreme%20polarisation%3F%20On%20caste%20atrocities%20and%20on%20restoring%20the%20idea%20of%20fraternity%3F%20The%20idea%20of%20having%20such%20commissions%20can%20sometimes%20be%20controversial%20and%20rake%20up%20wounds%20of%20the%20past%20at%20a%20time%20of%20a%20majoritarian%20sway%20in%20the%20polity%2C%20but%20this%20could%20also%20offer%20a%20way%20out%20of%20some%20intractable%20problems%20and%20help%20acknowledge%20societal%20divides.%20If%20nothing%20else%2C%20it%20may%20help%20frame%20the%20problem%20and%20underline%20a%20commitment%20to%20build%20bridges%20in%20a%20plural%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702285403000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F07121155%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_inside_bulidings_02.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffour-important-takeaways-from-the-supreme-court-ruling-on-jammu-and-kashmir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20pronouncements%20and%20utterances%20today%20will%20have%20serious%20implications%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20two%20northern-most%20union%20territories%2C%20but%20also%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffour-important-takeaways-from-the-supreme-court-ruling-on-jammu-and-kashmir%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mumbai%20businessman%20held%20hostage%20in%20his%20house%2C%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20looted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702285018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105899917%2Cimgsize-59398.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-businessman-held-hostage-in-his-house-rs-55-lakh-looted%2Farticleshow%2F105899917.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-businessman-held-hostage-in-his-house-rs-55-lakh-looted%2Farticleshow%2F105899917.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mumbai%20businessman%20held%20hostage%20in%20his%20house%2C%20Rs%2055%20cr%20looted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702