s%20not%20justifying%2C%20and%20this%20context%20in%20no%20way%20excuses%20the%20targeting%20of%20Israeli%20civilians%20and%20migrant%20workers%20by%20Palestinians%20on%20October%207%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20scholars%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20letter%20gives%20examples%20of%20inflammatory%20or%20dehumanising%20language%20used%20in%20Israel%20against%20Gazans%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20including%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYehudaShaul%2Fstatus%2F1714301958607999071%5C%22%3Eallegedly%20used%20by%20Israeli%20journalists%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20by%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fliveblog_entry%2Fcogat-chief-addresses-gazans-you-wanted-hell-you-will-get-hell%2F%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20army%20major%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20notes%20that%20the%20use%20of%20such%20language%20puts%20Palestinians%20outside%20Gaza%2C%20such%20as%20those%20living%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20or%20those%20who%20were%20citizens%20of%20Israel%2C%20in%20danger%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComments%20made%20by%20an%20Israeli%20parliamentarian%20from%20the%20Israeli%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20Likud%20party%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FArielKallner%2Fstatus%2F1710769363119141268%5C%22%3Eseemingly%20seeking%20a%20second%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENakba%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20also%20mentioned%20in%20the%20letter.%20%3Cem%3ENakba%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20Arabic%20word%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20dispossession%20of%20Palestinians%20when%20Israel%20was%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20that%20genocide%20is%20a%20process%2C%20and%20we%20recognise%20that%20the%20stage%20is%20thus%20set%20for%20violence%20%3Cem%3Emore%3C%2Fem%3E%20severe%20than%20the%20Nakba%20and%20not%20spatially%20limited%20to%20Gaza%2C%20%5Bemphasis%20retained%5D%E2%80%9D%20the%20scholars%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnding%20their%20letter%20by%20urging%20immediate%20and%20concerted%20action%20to%20prevent%20a%20genocide%2C%20the%20scholars%20said%20that%20governments%20must%20take%20six%20steps%20to%20achieve%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20included%20imposing%20an%20arms%20embargo%20on%20Israel%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpressuring%20the%20Israeli%20government%20to%20stop%20immediately%E2%80%9D%20the%20settler%20violence%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20issuing%20arrest%20warrants%20against%20perpetrators%20of%20mass%20violence%20both%20Palestinian%20and%20Israeli%2C%20and%20initiating%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20process%20in%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20based%20on%20a%20truthful%20reckoning%20with%20Israeli%20mass%20violence%20against%20Palestinians%20since%20the%201948%20Nakba.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20urged%20Holocaust%20and%20genocide%20studies%20scholars%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20a%20clear%20stance%20against%20Israeli%20mass%20violence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FavT8I2UADKA%3Fsi%3DEwwG9KOqRDZa1AFi%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20is%20reproduced%20in%20full%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStatement%20of%20Scholars%20in%20Holocaust%20and%20Genocide%20Studies%20on%20Mass%20Violence%20in%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20since%207%20October%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDecember%209%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20scholars%20of%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20genocide%2C%20and%20mass%20violence%2C%20feel%20compelled%20to%20warn%20of%20the%20danger%20of%20genocide%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20attack%20on%20Gaza.%20We%20also%20note%20that%2C%20should%20the%20Israeli%20attack%20continue%20and%20escalate%2C%20Palestinians%20under%20Israeli%20military%20occupation%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20East%20Jerusalem%20and%20Palestinian%20citizens%20of%20Israel%20face%20grave%20danger%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20deeply%20saddened%20and%20concerned%20by%20the%20mass%20murder%20of%20over%201%2C200%20Israelis%20and%20migrant%20workers%20by%20Hamas%2C%20the%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20and%20others%20on%207%20October%2C%20with%20more%20than%20830%20civilians%20among%20them.%20We%20also%20note%20the%20evidence%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.phr.org.il%2Fen%2Fgender-based-violence-eng%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egender-based%20and%20sexual%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0during%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20wounding%20of%20thousands%20of%20Israelis%2C%20the%20destruction%20of%20Israeli%20kibbutzim%20and%20towns%2C%20and%20the%20abduction%20of%20more%20than%20240%20hostages%20into%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20These%20acts%20constitute%20war%20crimes%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity.%20We%20recognize%20that%20violence%20in%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20did%20not%20begin%20on%207%20October.%20If%20we%20are%20to%20try%20to%20understand%20the%20mass%20murder%20of%207%20October%2C%20we%20should%20place%20it%20within%20the%20context%20of%20Israeli%20settler%20colonialism%2C%20Israeli%20military%20occupation%20violence%20against%20Palestinians%20since%201967%2C%20the%20sixteen-year%20siege%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20since%202007%2C%20and%20the%20rise%20to%20power%20in%20Israel%20in%20the%20last%20year%20of%20a%20government%20made%20up%20of%20politicians%20who%20speak%20proudly%20about%20Jewish%20supremacy%20and%20exclusionary%20nationalism.%20Explaining%20is%20not%20justifying%2C%20and%20this%20context%20in%20no%20way%20excuses%20the%20targeting%20of%20Israeli%20civilians%20and%20migrant%20workers%20by%20Palestinians%20on%207%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20also%20deeply%20saddened%20and%20concerned%20by%20the%20Israeli%20attack%20on%20Gaza%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Hamas%20attack.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20assault%20has%20caused%20death%20and%20destruction%20on%20an%20unprecedented%20level%2C%20according%20to%20a%20New%20York%20Times%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F11%2F25%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-gaza-death-toll.html%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%2026%20November.%20In%20two%20months%2C%20the%20Israeli%20assault%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2016%2C000%20Palestinians%20(with%20thousands%20more%20buried%20under%20the%20rubble)%E2%80%94nearly%20half%20of%20them%20children%20and%20youth%2C%20with%20a%20Palestinian%20child%20killed%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2F22%2Fisrael%2Fgaza-hostilities-take-horrific-toll-children%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevery%20ten%20minutes%20on%20average%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0before%20the%20ceasefire%E2%80%94and%20wounded%20over%2040%2C000.%20Considering%20that%20the%20total%20population%20of%20Gaza%20stands%20at%202.3%20million%20people%2C%20the%20killing%20rate%20so%20far%20is%20about%200.7%20percent%20in%20less%20than%20two%20months.%20The%20killing%20rate%20of%20civilians%20in%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20bombing%20and%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20areas%20most%20affected%20by%20the%20violence%20are%20probably%20similar%E2%80%94but%20over%20a%20longer%20period%20of%20time.%20A%20number%20of%20experts%20have%20therefore%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbs.org%2Fnewshour%2Fworld%2Fpalestinians-fear-gaza-will-be-an-uninhabitable-moonscape-after-war-ends%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Israel%E2%80%99s%20attack%20on%20Gaza%20as%20the%20most%20intense%20and%20deadliest%20of%20its%20kind%20since%20World%20War%20II%2C%20but%20while%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20attack%20on%20Ukraine