%E2%80%9Cethnic%20cleansing%E2%80%9D%20of%20more%20than%20750%2C000%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20destruction%20of%20hundreds%20of%20villages%20and%20towns%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20in%20the%201948%20war%2C%20when%20Israel%20was%20established.%20The%20language%20that%20member%20of%20the%20Israeli%20Knesset%20(parliament)%20Ariel%20Kallner%20from%20the%20ruling%20Likud%20party%20used%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FArielKallner%2Fstatus%2F1710769363119141268%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0post%20on%207%20October%20is%20instructive%3A%20%E2%80%9CNakba%20to%20the%20enemy%20now.%20%E2%80%A6%20Now%2C%20only%20one%20goal%3A%20Nakba!%20Nakba%20that%20will%20overshadow%20the%20Nakba%20of%201948.%20Nakba%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Nakba%20to%20whoever%20dares%20to%20join%20%5Bthem%5D.%E2%80%9D%20We%20know%20that%20genocide%20is%20a%20process%2C%20and%20we%20recognize%20that%20the%20stage%20is%20thus%20set%20for%20violence%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emore%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0severe%20than%20the%20Nakba%20and%20not%20spatially%20limited%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20time%20for%20concerted%20action%20to%20prevent%20genocide%20is%20now.%20We%20call%20on%20governments%20to%20uphold%20their%20legal%20obligations%20under%20the%20UN%20Convention%20on%20the%20Prevention%20and%20Punishment%20of%20the%20Crime%20of%20Genocide%20to%20intervene%20and%20prevent%20genocide%20(Article%201)%20by%20(1)%20implementing%20an%20arms%20embargo%20on%20Israel%3B%20(2)%20working%20to%20end%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20assault%20on%20Gaza%3B%20(3)%20pressuring%20the%20Israeli%20government%20to%20stop%20immediately%20the%20intensifying%20army%20and%20settler%20violence%20against%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20East%20Jerusalem%2C%20which%20constitute%20clear%20violations%20of%20international%20law%3B%20(4)%20demanding%20the%20continued