that%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20police%20had%20stated%20that%20the%20November%2022%20blast%20looked%20like%20a%20handiwork%20of%20ULFA-I%2C%20the%20outfit%20has%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20it%20only%20after%20the%20December%209%20blast.%20These%20blasts%20came%20as%20a%20reminder%20to%20the%20public%20of%20the%20dark%20days%20of%20insurgency%20in%20the%201990s%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20stating%20that%20insurgency%20in%20Assam%20is%20under%20control%2C%20some%20areas%20of%20the%20state%20have%20seen%20removal%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20(Special%20Powers)%20Act.%20However%2C%20the%20districts%20where%20these%20attacks%20had%20occurred%20are%20still%20under%20the%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20ULFA-I%E2%80%99s%20letter%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnagalandpost.com%2Findex.php%2Fulfa-i-claims-responsibility-for-recent-grenade-blasts%2F%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20DGP%20of%20%E2%80%9Carrogance%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20personal%20animosity%20with%20Assam%20police.%20They%20all%20are%20sons%20of%20our%20soil.%20But%20the%20recent%20blasts%20were%20to%20prove%20to%20the%20recent%20DGP%20of%20Assam%20GP%20Singh%20that%20Assam%20Police%20is%20not%20personal%20property.%20Using%20and%20showing%20them%20to%20be%20his%20own%20personal%20property%20and%20power%20shows%20how%20ill-intentioned%20he%20is.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20previous%20DGP%20of%20Assam%2C%20Bhaskar%20Jyoti%20Mahanta%2C%20never%20did%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20arrogance%20shown%20by%20GP%20Singh%20by%20treating%20the%20Assam%20Police%20as%20his%20ancestral%20property%20has%20hurt%20the%20self-respect%20of%20the%20officers%2Fmembers%20working%20in%20the%20Assam%20Police%20and%20his%20arrogance%20cannot%20be%20acceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20further%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%2C%20active%20on%20X%2C%20has%20been%20sharing%20not%20only%20photos%20of%20youth%20surrendering%20to%20the%20state%20police%20after%20having%20deserted%20ULFA-I%20but%20has%20also%20been%20issuing%20appeals%20of%20family%20members%20who%20have%20left%20them%20to%20join%20militancy%20in%20recent%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702283454000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11133017%2FScreenshot-2023-12-11-at-1.29.01.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdgp-treats-assam-police-as-ancestral-property-ulfa-i-takes-responsibility-for-warning-blasts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20letter%2C%20the%20anti-talks%20faction%20of%20the%20outfit%20accused%20the%20top%20cop%20G.P.%20Singh%20of%20'arrogance.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdgp-treats-assam-police-as-ancestral-property-ulfa-i-takes-responsibility-for-warning-blasts%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20EU%20Plans%20to%20Regulate%20Artificial%20Intelligence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11124207%2Fimage-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20that%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Ft-42133476%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20have%20in%20almost%20all%20areas%20of%20life%20is%20enormous.%20While%20there%20are%20huge%20opportunities%20for%20commercial%20enterprises%2C%20there%20are%20also%20risks%20for%20users.%20Even%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20the%20developer%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fchatgpt%2Ft-67348272%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20language%20model%2C%20has%20made%20such%20warnings.%20Some%20scientists%20even%20argue%20that%20there%20could%20be%20a%20threat%20to%20humans%20if%20artificial%20intelligence%20develops%20aggressive%20applications%20beyond%20our%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20the%20EU%20set%20out%20to%20be%20the%20first%20major%20economic%20region%20worldwide%20to%20develop%20comprehensive%20regulations%20for%20AI.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20achieve%20comprehensible%2C%20transparent%2C%20fair%2C%20safe%20and%20environmentally%20friendly%20AI%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Feuropean-commission%2Ft-17455066%5C%22%3EEuropean%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20draft%20legislation.%20But%20this%20need%20not%20hinder%20development%20opportunities%20for%20AI%20startups%2C%20EU%20Industry%20Commissioner%20Thierry%20Breton%20said%20after%20the%20Commission%2C%20European%20Parliament%20representatives%20and%20the%20member%20state%20Council%20agreed%20on%20the%20proposal%20in%20what%20is%20known%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctrilogue%E2%80%9D%20meeting%20between%20the%20three%20entities%2C%20which%20must%20now%20be%20approved%20by%20a%20committee%20vote%20and%20confirmed%20by%20the%20plenary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20what%20will%20be%20regulated%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EU%20formulated%20a%20neutral%20definition%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20technology%20used.%20This%20is%20intended%20to%20enable%20the%20law%20to%20be%20applied%20to%20future%20developments%20and%20the%20next%20generations%20of%20AI.%20The%20rules%20for%20specific%20AI%20products%20can%20then%20be%20issued%20in%20the%20form%20of%20simple%20ordinances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20products%20are%20divided%20into%20four%20risk%20classes%3A%20Unacceptable%20risk%2C%20high%20risk%2C%20generative%20AI%20and%20limited%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProhibited%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESystems%20that%20force%20people%20to%20change%20their%20behaviour%2C%20for%20example%20toys%20that%20encourage%20children%20to%20perform%20dangerous%20actions%2C%20fall%20into%20the%20unacceptable%20category.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20remote-controlled%20biometric%20recognition%20systems%20that%20recognise%20faces%20in%20real%20time.%20AI%20applications%20that%20divide%20people%20into%20classes%20based%20on%20certain%20characteristics%20such%20as%20gender%2C%20skin%20color%2C%20social%20behaviour%20or%20origin%20will%20be%20banned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExceptions%20will%20be%20made%20for%20the%20military%2C%20intelligence%20services%20and%20investigative%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOnly%20with%20approval%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20programs%20that%20pose%20a%20high%20risk%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20a%20review%20before%20they%20are%20approved%20for%20the%20market%20to%20prevent%20any%20impact%20on%20fundamental%20rights.%20These%20risky%20applications%20include%20self-driving%20cars%2C%20medical%20technology%2C%20energy%20supply%2C%20aviation%20and%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20they%20also%20include%20border%20surveillance%2C%20migration%20control%2C%20police%20work%2C%20the%20management%20of%20company%20personnel%20and%20recording%20biometric%20data%20in%20ID%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrograms%20intended%20to%20help%20with%20the%20interpretation%20and%20application%20of%20European%20AI%20law%20are%20also%20classified%20as%20high-risk%20and%20subject%20to%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransparency%20for%20generative%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20EU%20legislators%2C%20systems%20that%20generate%20new%20content%20and%20analyse%20vast%20amounts%20of%20data%2C%20such%20as%20generative%20AI%20products%20like%20ChatGPT%20from%20Microsoft%20subsidiary%20OpenAI%2C%20pose%20a%20medium%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompanies%20are%20obliged%20to%20be%20transparent%20about%20how%20their%20AI%20works%20and%20how%20it%20prevents%20illegal%20content%20from%20being%20generated.%20They%20must%20also%20disclose%20how%20the%20AI%20was%20trained%20and%20which%20copyright-protected%20data%20was%20used.%20All%20content%20generated%20with%20ChatGPT%2C%20for%20example%2C%20must%20be%20labelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELimited%20regulations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20new%20EU%20rules%2C%20programs%20that%20manipulate%20and%20recreate%20videos%2C%20audio%20or%20photos%20pose%20only%20a%20low%20risk.%20This%20also%20includes%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20fakes%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20are%20already%20commonplace%20on%20many%20social%20media%20platforms.%20Service%20programs%20that%20look%20after%20customers%20also%20belong%20to%20this%20risk%20class%2C%20with%20only%20minimal%20transparency%20rules%20to%20be%20applied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsers%20must%20simply%20be%20made%20aware%20they%20are%20interacting%20with%20an%20AI%20application%20and%20not%20with%20humans.%20They%20can%20then%20decide%20for%20themselves%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20continue%20using%20the%20AI%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20will%20the%20new%20law%20take%20force%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20long%20days%20of%20negotiations%2C%20the%20three%20main%20EU%20institutions%20%E2%80%94%20the%20European%20Commission%2C%20Parliament%20and%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20%E2%80%94%20have%20agreed%20on%20a%20preliminary%20draft%20law%2C%20which%20does%20not%20yet%20contain%20all%20the%20technically%20necessary%20provisions.%20This%20must%20now%20be%20formally%20approved%20by%20the%20European%20Parliament%20and%20the%20Council%2C%20the%20representative%20body%20of%20the%2027%20member%20states%2C%20which%20is%20due%20to%20take%20place%20in%20April%202024%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20legislative%20period.%20Member%20states%20will%20then%20have%20two%20years%20to%20transpose%20the%20AI%20law%20into%20national%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20rapid%20developments%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20that%20the%20EU%20rules%20will%20already%20be%20outdated%20by%20the%20time%20they%20come%20into%20force%2C%20German%20Christian%20Democratic%20MEP%20Axel%20Voss%20warned%20before%20the%20whole%20process%20even%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20now%20offers%20paid%20programs%20that%20can%20be%20modified%20by%20users%20according%20to%20their%20wishes%20and%20specifications.%20According%20to%20UK%20broadcaster%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20research%2C%20these%20%E2%80%9Ctoolkits%E2%80%9D%20can%20for%20instance%20do%20things%20like%20write%20fraudulent%20emails%20for%20hackers%20or%20people%20with%20criminal%20intentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20everything%20that%20has%20been%20agreed%20upon%20works%20in%20practice.%20The%20ideas%20in%20the%20AI%20law%20will%20only%20be%20workable%20if%20we%20have%20legal%20certainty%2C%20harmonised%20standards%2C%20clear%20guidelines%20and%20clear%20enforcement%2C%E2%80%9D%20Voss%20said%20in%20Brussels%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20has%20the%20tech%20sector%20reacted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Computer%20and%20Communications%20Industry%20Association%20in%20Europe%20(CCIA)%20warned%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20EU%E2%80%99s%20compromise%20proposal%20is%20%E2%80%9Chalf-baked%E2%80%9D%20and%20could%20over-regulate%20many%20aspects%20of%20AI.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20final%20AI%20Act%20lacks%20the%20vision%20and%20ambition%20that%20European%20tech%20startups%20and%20businesses%20are%20displaying%20right%20now.%20It%20might%20even%20end%20up%20chasing%20away%20the%20European%20champions%20that%20the%20EU%20so%20desperately%20wants%20to%20empower%2C%E2%80%9D%20CCIA%20Policy%20Manager%20Boniface%20de%20Champris%20told%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumer%20advocates%20from%20the%20European%20Consumer%20Organisation%20(BEUC)%20lobbying%20group%20also%20criticized%20the%20draft%20law.%20Their%20initial%20assessment%20said%20the%20law%20is%20too%20lax%20because%20it%20gives%20companies%20too%20much%20room%20for%20self-regulation%20without%20providing%20sufficient%20guard%20rails%20for%20virtual%20assistants%2C%20toys%20or%20generative%20AI%20such%20as%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20the%20EU%20now%20compare%20to%20other%20countries%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Funited-states-of-america%2Ft-19065189%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Funited-kingdom%2Ft-60783992%5C%22%3EUnited%20Kingdom%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2020%20other%20countries%20have%20issued%20data%20protection%20rules%20and%20recommendations%20for%20AI%20developers%2C%20but%20none%20of%20these%20are%20legally%20binding%2C%20the%20expectation%20being%20that%20big%20tech%20companies%20working%20on%20AI%20should%20voluntarily%20monitor%20themselves.%20A%20%E2%80%9CSafety%20Institute%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20US%20is%20meant%20to%20assess%20the%20risks%20of%20AI%20applications%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fjoe-biden%2Ft-55668302%5C%22%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20instructed%20developers%20to%20disclose%20their%20tests%20if%20national%20security%2C%20public%20health%20or%20safety%20are%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20China%2C%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20for%20private%20customers%20and%20companies%20is%20severely%20restricted%20because%20the%20communist%20regime%20is%20afraid%20that%20it%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20censor%20learning%20systems%20as%20easily%20as%20censored%20the%20internet.%20ChatGPT%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20not%20available%20in%20China.%20However%2C%20facial%20recognition%20is%20already%20being%20used%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhow-the-eu-plans-to-regulate-artificial-intelligence%2Fa-67679594%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3EDW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702283377000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11124207%2Fimage-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fhow-the-eu-plans-to-regulate-artificial-intelligence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20EU%20Parliament%20and%20the%20member%20states%20agreed%20on%20a%20draft%20of%20their%20new%20AI%20Act.%20So%20what%20exactly%20will%20the%20landmark%20regulations%20entail%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fhow-the-eu-plans-to-regulate-artificial-intelligence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karan%20Johar%20shares%20his%20take%20on%20gender%20politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702283372000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105898875%2Cimgsize-36118.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanimal-karan-johar-shares-his-take-on-gender-politics%2Farticleshow%2F105898832.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105898832.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20buzz%20around%20Ranbir%20Kapoor's%20latest%20film%2C%20%E2%80%98Animal%2C%E2%80%99%20has%20taken%20center%20stage%2C%20not%20just%20for%20its%20box%20office%20success%20but%20also%20for%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20its%20alleged%20glorification%20of%20misogyny%20and%20toxic%20masculinity.%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20Karan%20Johar%20delved%20into%20the%20complex%20realm%20of%20gender%20politics%2C%20shedding%20light%20on%20the%20film%20and%20its%20director%2C%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga.%20Johar%20acknowledged%20the%20criticism%20%E2%80%98Animal%E2%80%99%20has%20faced%2C%20comparing%20it%20to%20the%20evolving%20perspective%20he%20has%20gained%20over%20the%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanimal-karan-johar-shares-his-take-on-gender-politics%2Farticleshow%2F105898832.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CSK%20Strategy%20At%20IPL%202024%20Auction%3A%20Which%20Players%20Will%20Dhoni%20And%20Co.%20Go%20For%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20Auction%202024%2C%20set%20to%20be%20conducted%20on%20December%2019%20in%20Dubai%2C%20all%20eyes%20will%20be%20on%20MS%20Dhoni's%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK).%20While%20the%20IPL%202024%20season%20is%20expected%20to%20get%20underway%20in%20March%20next%20year%2C%20CSK's%20title%20defence%20kicks%20off%20with%20the%20auction%20itself.%20With%20other%20title%20rivals%20certain%20to%20strengthen%20their%20squad%2C%20the%20Chennai%20outfit%20must%20get%20the%20balance%20of%20their%20squad%20right%20for%20the%20upcoming%20campaign%20if%20they%20are%20to%20retain%20their%20crown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeading%20into%20the%202024%20IPL%20Season%2C%20the%20Super%20Kings%20have%20already%20released%20some%20big%20names%20like%20Ben%20Stokes%2C%20Ambati%20Rayudu%2C%20Dwayne%20Pretorius%20and%20Kyle%20Jamieson.%20Fringe%20players%20like%20Sisanda%20Magala%2C%20Bhagath%20Varma%2C%20Akash%20Singh%20and%20Subhranshu%20Senapati%20have%20also%20been%20released%2C%20leaving%20CSK%20with%20a%20list%20of%2019%20retained%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cstrong%3ECSK's%20retained%20players%20list%20for%20IPL%202024%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMS%20Dhoni%20(captain%20and%20wicket-keeper)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMoeen%20Ali%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDeepak%20Chahar%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDevon%20Conway%20(wicket-keeper)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETushar%20Deshpande%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShivam%20Dube%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERuturaj%20Gaikwad%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERajvardhan%20Hangargekar%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAjay%20Mandal%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMukesh%20Choudhary%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMatheesha%20Pathirana%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAjinkya%20Rahane%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShaik%20Rasheed%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMitchell%20Santner%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESimarjeet%20Singh%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENishant%20Sindhu%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrashant%20Solanki%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMaheesh%20Theekshana%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20leaves%20CSK%20above%20the%20team%20floor%20limit%20of%2018%20and%20with%20a%20purse%20of%2031.4%20crore%20INR%20to%20strengthen%20their%20squad%20at%20the%20IPL%202024%20mini-auction%20in%20Dubai%20and%20enough%20financial%20muscle%20to%20flex%20to%20go%20for%20the%20big-money%20players%20they%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20maximum%20of%20six%20slots%20left%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20squad%2C%20the%20big%20question%20that%20crops%20up%20is%20who%20will%20MS%20Dhoni%20and%20the%20CSK%20management%20target%20at%20the%20upcoming%20auction%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECSK's%20strategy%20for%20IPL%202024%20auction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSK%20has%20been%20known%20for%20making%20bold%20moves%20at%20IPL%20auctions%20and%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20their%20gambles%20have%20paid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurn%20the%20clock%20back%20to%20the%20inaugural%20IPL%20Auction%20back%20in%202008%2C%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20pulled%20off%20a%20masterstroke%20of%20a%20move.%20Not%20succumbing%20to%20the%20allure%20of%20an%20icon%20player%2C%20CSK%20opted%20to%20safeguard%20their%20purse%20for%20a%20then-record%20bid%20of%20US%24%201.5%20million%20for%20one%20MS%20Dhoni%20and%20the%20rest%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni%20would%20go%20on%20to%20lead%20the%20team%20to%2010%20finals%20in%20CSK's%2014%20seasons%2C%20winning%20five%20IPL%20titles%20in%20the%20process%20-%20the%20joint-most%20alongside%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20who%20have%20played%20all%2016%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSK%20have%20managed%20to%20retain%20the%20entirety%20of%20their%20regular%20starting%20XI%20from%20the%20IPL%202023%20-%20their%20last%20title-winning%20season%20-%20barring%20for%20the%20experienced%20Ambati%20Rayadu%2C%20who%20retired%20after%20last%20season's%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERayadu%20played%20all%2016%20of%20CSK's%20matches%20in%20IPL%202023%20and%20replacing%20the%20seasoned%20campaigner%20in%20the%20middle%20order%20will%20be%20MS%20Dhoni's%20top%20priority%20in%20the%20pre-season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFortunately%20for%20CSK%2C%20there'll%20be%20plenty%20of%20options%20available.%20While%20Kiwi%20duo%20of%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20and%20Daryl%20Mitchell%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20are%20coming%20off%20impressive%20campaigns%20at%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%2C%20are%20potent%20options%20from%20the%20overseas%20list%2C%20the%20likes%20of%20Manish%20Pandey%2C%20Shahrukh%20Khan%20and%20Karun%20Nair%20will%20be%20on%20the%20cards%20if%20CSK%20decides%20to%20go%20the%20domestic%20player%20route%20to%20fill%20in%20Rayadu's%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahrukh%20Khan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20released%20by%20Punjab%20Kings%2C%20presents%20a%20particularly%20interesting%20case.%20CSK%20bid%20a%20whopping%208.75%20crores%20for%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20batter%20before%20finally%20conceding%20him%20to%20PBKS%20for%209.00%20crores%20at%20the%20IPL%202022%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSK%20has%20a%20track%20record%20for%20going%20back%20for%20players%20they%20have%20missed%20at%20auctions%20and%20Khan%20being%20a%20Chennai-native%20also%20adds%20some%20added%20incentive%20for%20the%20CSK%20management%20to%20make%20the%20move%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDaryl%20Mitchell%2C%20too%2C%20presents%20an%20interesting%20choice%20due%20to%20his%20ability%20to%20contribute%20as%20a%20sixth%20bowler.%20Furthermore%2C%20Dwayne%20Pretorius%20and%20Kyle%20Jamieson's%20departure%20also%20leaves%20space%20for%20a%20fast-bowling%20all-rounder%20in%20the%20squad.%20Mitchell%2C%20however%2C%20won't%20come%20cheap%20after%20his%20World%20Cup%20exploits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20season%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20specialist%20pace%20bowler%20in%20the%20death%20overs%20hurt%20CSK%20in%20certain%20matches%20and%20Dhoni%20will%20be%20eager%20to%20plug%20the%20hole.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Men%20in%20Yellow%20can%20also%20do%20with%20a%20little%20more%20firepower%20in%20their%20pace%20battery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepak%20Chahar%20and%20Matheesha%20Pathirana%20did%20exceptionally%20well%20last%20season%20for%20CSK%20with%20the%20new%20ball%20but%20the%20former's%20injury%20record%20and%20the%20latter's%20inexperience%20will%20be%20a%20reason%20for%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShardul%20Thakur%20and%20Josh%20Hazlewood%2C%20both%20former%20CSK%20players%2C%20can%20both%20be%20ideal%20answers%20and%20will%20be%20available%20to%20bid%20for%20at%20the%20maximum%20base%20price%20of%20INR%202%20crore.%20Thakur%20was%20CSK's%20top%20wicket-taker%20during%20their%20title%20win%20in%202021.%20Harshal%20Patel%20may%20be%20another%20player%20the%20CSK%20strategists%20will%20be%20looking%20into%20considering%20his%20record%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAussie%20speedster%20Mitchell%20Starc%20is%20expected%20to%20attract%20the%20big%20bids%20from%20multiple%20teams%20and%20may%20present%20an%20interesting%20option%20should%20CSK%20decide%20to%20splurge%20big%20to%20rope%20in%20a%20proven%20match-winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSK%20may%20have%20done%20well%20even%20without%20Ben%20Stokes'%20services%20last%20season%20but%20having%20a%20proven%20match-winner%20in%20the%20squad%20is%20a%20luxury%20very%20few%20teams%20will%20pass%20up%20on%20if%20the%20option%20presents%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20likes%20of%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20and