%20the%20defamation%20case%20she%20has%20filed%20against%20Jai%20Dehadrai%20and%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20in%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20was%20taken%20up%20for%20hearing%20on%20Monday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20her%20expulsion%2C%20Moitra%20had%20said%20that%20parliament%20had%20behaved%20like%20a%20%E2%80%9Ckangaroo%20court%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegation%20against%20Moitra%2C%20for%20which%20she%20was%20expelled%2C%20was%20that%20she%20shared%20her%20Lok%20Sabha%20portal%20login%20and%20password%20details%20with%20Dubai-based%20business%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%2C%20who%20in%20turn%20uploaded%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20questions%20on%20her%20behalf%20in%20return%20for%20cash%20and%20gifts.%20The%20questions%20were%20majorly%20those%20in%20which%20the%20Hiranandani%20group%20had%20business%20interests%20that%20clashed%20with%20those%20of%20business%20tycoon%20Gautam%20Adani.%20The%20allegations%2C%20of%20what%20is%20being%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccash-for-query%E2%80%9D%20scam%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20were%20made%20by%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20bete%20noire%2C%20Nishikant%20Dubey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoitra%20has%20consistently%20held%20that%20these%20allegations%20are%20spurious%2C%20and%20that%20while%20she%20did%20share%20her%20password%2C%20that%20is%20a%20common%20practice%20amongst%20MPs%20as%20they%20do%20not%20have%20the%20time%20to%20upload%20questions%20on%20her%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20come%20down%20hard%20on%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20for%20the%20way%20parliament%20was%20conducted%20on%20Friday%2C%20when%20Moitra%20was%20expelled.%20After%20giving%20members%20of%20parliament%20only%20two%20hours%20to%20read%20the%20104-page%20ethics%20committee%20report%20after%20it%20was%20tabled%2C%20a%2030-minute%20discussion%20was%20scheduled.%20But%20Moitra%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20speak%20and%20she%20was%20expelled%20even%20before%20the%20discussion%20time%20was%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%