%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20Congress%20needs%20to%20take%20note%20of%20is%20that%20the%20shift%20of%20the%20vote%20of%20independents%20and%20smaller%20parties%20has%20been%20mainly%20towards%C2%A0%20the%20BJP%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20past%20decade.%20Over%20these%20four%20elections%2C%20approximately%2010%25%20of%20the%20vote%20that%20used%20to%20go%20to%20smaller%20parties%20and%20independents%20has%20shifted%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%20But%20of%20the%20this%2010%25%2C%20two%20thirds%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20BJP%20alone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20impact%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20relentless%20drive%20to%20polarise%20the%20vote%20on%20communal%20lines%20has%20had.%20It%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20create%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20But%20it%20has%20sounded%20a%20warning%20to%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20Indians%20who%20have%20so%20far%20taken%20Indian%20secularism%20and%20ethnic%20diversity%20for%20granted%20that%20both%20are%20now%20in%20deadly%20danger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20secular%20India%2C%20forming%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20was%20an%20essential%20first%20step.%20But%20its%20hopes%20will%20be%20dashed%20if%20it%20remains%20the%20last.%20Congress%20present%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20statement%20that%20INDIA%20needs%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erebuild%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erevive%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20itself%E2%80%9D%20shows%20how%20close%20INDIA%20had%20come%20to%20becoming%20moribund%20when%20the%20shock%20of%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20defeats%20hit%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ET%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehat%20revival%20needs%20a%20clearly%20articulated%20and%20well%20publicised%20basis%20for%20the%20allocation%20of%20seats%20among%20its%20members%3B%20a%20common%20programme%3B%20a%20common%20platform%20from%20which%20to%20project%20it%3B%20and%20a%20strong%20research%20team%20that%20identifies%20issues%20and%20collects%20the%20data%20needed%20to%20expose%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20meet%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20promises%2C%20and%20to%20show%20how%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20meet%20the%20peoples%E2%80%99%20most%20pressing%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbove%20all%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20show%20its%20unity%20in%20action.%20In%20the%20last%20three%20months%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20administration%20has%20attacked%20every%20leader%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20who%20is%20capable%20of%20formulating%20such%20a%20response%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20or%20Mahua%20Moitra%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewith%20not%20a%20peep%20out%20of%20any%20member%20of%20the%20alliance%20in%20their%20defence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20absolute%20silence%20is%20creating%20a%20walkover%20for%20Modi%20and%20his%20brand%20of%20Hindutva%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20INDIA%20has%20only%20four%20months%20left%20in%20which%20to%20break%20its%20paralysis%20and%20create%20the%20alternative%20image%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20future%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20people%20are%20hungering%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPrem%20Shankar%20Jha%20is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702281635000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04152158%2FGALn98pbMAAFBeo.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-cause-of-the-bjps-victories-in-state-polls-is-mundane-misreading-it-will-only-benefit-them%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rise%20in%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20has%20not%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20Congress'%20voter%20base%20but%20that%20of%20other%20smaller%20parties%2C%20data%20shows.%22%2C%22author