2C%20filed%20by%20J%26amp%3BK-centric%20parties%2C%20groups%20and%20individuals%20who%20termed%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cunilateral%E2%80%9D%20decision%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20mosaic%20of%20illegalities%E2%80%9D%2C%20had%20urged%20the%20apex%20court%20to%20restore%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SC%20had%20clubbed%20the%20petitions%20and%20a%20new%20bench%20comprising%20five%20senior-most%20judges%20of%20the%20apex%20court%20was%20formed%20on%20July%203%20this%20year.%20It%20heard%20the%20matter%20over%20a%20period%20of%2016%20days%20in%20August%20and%20September%2C%20and%20reserved%20its%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20Faesal%2C%20the%202010-batch%20IAS%20officer%20from%20Kashmir%2C%20was%20the%20lead%20petitioner%20in%20the%20case.%20He%20resigned%20from%20the%20civil%20services%20in%202018%20to%20protest%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunabated%20killings%20in%20Kashmir%E2%80%9D%20and%20briefly%20toyed%20with%20politics.%20Faesal%2C%20however%2C%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20petition%20after%20his%20reinstatement%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20IAS%20officer%20was%20among%20several%20dozens%20of%20political%20detainees%2C%20which%20included%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20three%20former%20chief%20ministers%2C%20former%20ministers%2C%20MLAs%2C%20MLCs%2C%20lawyers%2C%20activists%20and%20others%20who%20were%20taken%20into%20preventive%20custody%20on%20August%204%2C%202019%2C%20a%20day%20before%20Article%20370%20was%20read%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20woke%20up%20amid%20a%20communication%20blackhole%20and%20unprecedented%20security%20measures.%20A%20strict%20curfew%20was%20imposed%20overnight%20and%20shoot-at-sight%20orders%20were%20reportedly%20issued%20(though%20denied%20by%20the%20government)%20to%20prevent%20any%20street%20protests%20that%20defined%20Kashmiri%20rage%20in%20the%20years%20before%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMobile%20phone%20and%20internet%20connectivity%20remained%20blocked%20for%20months%2C%20education%20and%20healthcare%20sectors%20suffered%20the%20brunt%20while%20hundreds%20of%20Kashmiri%20leaders%20and%20political%20activists%20were%20thrown%20into%20jails%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20continue%20to%20remain%20incarcerated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20newest%20union%20territory%20came%20out%20of%20crippling%20restrictions%20in%202020%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20started%20tightening%20its%20grip%20by%20rolling%20out%20a%20series%20of%20new%20rules%20and%20laws%20which%20have%20altered%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20political%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20decision%20to%20read%20down%20Article%20370%20was%20yet%20to%20be%20decided%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20pushed%20J%26amp%3BK%20on%20a%20new%20trajectory%2C%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20its%20people%20or%20the%20approval%20of%20courts%2C%20while%20eyeing%20a%20foothold%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20only%20Muslim-majority%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20new%20domicile%20and%20land%20laws%20that%20have%20trampled%20on%20the%20special%20rights%20enjoyed%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20citizens%20to%20the%20redrawing%20of%20assembly%20and%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20through%20delimitation%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20steamrolled%20a%20series%20of%20changes%20which%20have%20reset%20J%26amp%3BK%20relationship%20with%20the%20Union%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20some%2C%20these%20drastic%20and%20dramatic%20changes%20have%20turned%20J%26amp%3BK%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98peaceful%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98prosperous%E2%80%99%20region%20but%20for%20many%20others%2C%20the%20move%20to%20read%20down%20Article%20370%20has%20alienated%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%20and%20widened%20the%20chasm%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20political%20front%2C%20J%26amp%3BK-centric%20parties%20such%20as%20the%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%20and%20People%E2%80%99s%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%20have%20reeled%20under%20a%20series%20of%20setbacks%20and%20defections%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20former%20Congress%20leader%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20and%20former%20PDP%20leader%20Altaf%20Bukhari%2C%20two%20new%20parties%20have%20appeared%20on%20the%20political%20horizon%20which%20are%20getting%20filled%20with%20NC%20and%20PDP%20renegades%2C%20under%20what%20some%20believe%20is%20a%20ploy%20to%20fragment%20the%20vote%20of%20Kashmiri%20Muslims%20even%20further%20once%20the%20elections%20are%20held%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20PDP%20leaders%20joining%20these%20new%20political%20formations%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20former%20chief%20minister%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20has%20openly%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20breaking%20her%20party%20using%20the%20threat%20of%20investigation%20agencies%2C%20a%20charge%20denied%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20president%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20was%20also%20grilled%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20scam%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20cricket%2C%20which%20has%20been%20termed%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitically%20motivated%E2%80%9D%20investigation%20by%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20only%20the%20politics%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20which%20has%20changed%20post%20August%205%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20orbits%20of%20%E2%80%98security%20threat%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98terror%20funding%E2%80%99%20that%20covered%20Kashmiri%20militants%20and%20separatists%20in%20the%20years%20before%20Article%20370%20revocation%20is%20now%20being%20used%20against%20academics%2C%20government%20officials%2C%20teachers%2C%20journalists%2C%20bankers%20and%20even%20policemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20believe%20that%20it%20is%20this%20reign%20of%20a%20sweeping%20crackdown%20by%20investigation%20agencies%20post%20Article%20370%20that%20has%20pushed%20Kashmir%20into%20a%20meaningful%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20verdict%20on%20Article%20370%20is%20expected%20to%20generate%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20and%20debate%2C%20especially%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20which%20has%20prompted%20the%20security%20agencies%20to%20firm%20up%20the%20preparedness%20to%20prevent%20any%20kind%20of%20protests%20or%20other%20%E2%80%98disturbances%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20and%20NC%20vice-president%20Omar%20Abdullah%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20local%20administration%20withdrew%20permission%20for%20a%20rally%20his%20party%20was%20planning%20to%20organise%20in%20north%20Kashmir%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOmar%20hoped%20that%20the%20SC%E2%80%99s%20decision%20would%20%E2%80%9Cfavour%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%9D%20while%20the%20PDP%20president%2C%20who%20has%20vociferously%20opposed%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20said%20that%20the%20SC%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20%E2%80%9Cmight%20not%20be%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20with%20top%20officials%20of%20civil%20and%20police%20administration%2C%20which%20was%20chaired%20by%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Vijay%20Kumar%20last%20week%2C%20forces%E2%80%99%20deployment%20has%20been%20stepped%20up%20in%20parts%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20while%20security%20agencies%20are%20also%20monitoring%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20undoing%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20and%20especially%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20it%20was%20done%2C%20has%20come%20as%20a%20historic%20betrayal%20for%20most%20J%26amp%3BK-centric%20parties%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20continue%20to%20cherish%20it%20as%20the%20delivery%20of%20its%20long-held%20promise%20of%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Constitution%2C%20One%20Flag%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E