es%20I%20would%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20headache%20but%20nothing%20major%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Falcohol-allergy-was-cancer-1825032%5C%22%3Eshe%20told%20%3Cem%3ENewsweek%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20suddenly%20I%20noticed%20my%20tolerance%20was%20a%20lot%20less%20and%20my%20night%20would%20end%20with%20vomiting%20every%20time%2C%20even%20just%20after%20three%20drinks.%20The%20following%20day%20would%20be%20even%20worse.%20I%20would%20feel%20extremely%20unwell.%20I%20thought%20I%20might%20be%20allergic%20to%20alcohol%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Ms%20Beguely%20was%20hospitalised%20twice%20after%20an%20evening%20out%20with%20friends%20and%20the%20symptoms%20became%20more%20prominent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20was%20misdiagnosed%20thrice%2C%20with%20doctors%20telling%20Ms%20Beguely%20that%20she%20has%20multiple%20skin%20conditions%20like%20eczema%20and%20dermatitis%20-%20common%20skin%20conditions%20that%20cause%20irritation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rashes%20ended%20up%20getting%20worse%20on%20a%20day-to-day%20basis%20and%20my%20face%20was%20completely%20covered.%20I%20was%20given%20medication%20and%20steroid%20cream%20but%20it%20never%20cleared%20up.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20I%20was%20even%20told%20I%20have%20irritable%20bowel%20syndrome%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20diagnosis%20happened%20after%20doctors%20spotted%20a%20lump%20on%20Ms%20Beguely's%20neck%20as%20she%20complained%20of%20neck%20pain.%20%26quot%3BA%20lump%20on%20my%20neck%20appeared%20and%20that%20was%20the%20giveaway.%20I%20went%20to%20a%20doctor%20complaining%20of%20a%20sore%20neck%20and%20I%20forgot%20to%20mention%20the%20lump.%20I%20told%20him%20about%20my%20other%20symptoms%20and%20he%20left%20me%20to%20look%20at%20my%20notes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20came%20back%2C%20he%20told%