cial%20media%2C%20commentaries%2C%20and%20other%20state%20media%20articles%20responding%20to%20the%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYu%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Shanghai%2C%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Ngari%20District%20People's%20Hospital%20and%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20ruptured%20liver%2C%20severe%20blood%20loss%2C%20and%20life-threatening%20injuries%2C%20state-affiliated%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.cn%2F2023-12-06%2Fdetail-imzxaqvq5671850.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Paper%20reported%20in%20a%20follow-up%20investigation%20on%20December%206.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20required%20surgery%20and%20a%20blood%20transfusion%2C%20but%20medical%20facilities%20there%20did%20not%20have%20enough%20supply%20of%20her%20blood%20type.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20relative%20of%20Yu%2C%20an%20aunt%20on%20her%20father's%20side%20of%20the%20family%2C%20called%20the%20Shanghai%20Municipal%20Health%20Commission%20for%20assistance%2C%20and%20the%20organization%20put%20together%20a%20team%20of%20doctors%20who%20coordinated%20blood%20donations%20to%20stabilize%20her%20condition%2C%20per%20The%20Paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2016%2C%20several%20dozen%20local%20civil%20servants%2C%20including%20police%20officers%20and%20firefighters%2C%20donated%20blood%20to%20Yu%2C%20whose%20life%20was%20eventually%20saved%2C%20The%20Paper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Paper%20wrote%20that%20these%20individuals%20had%20volunteered%2C%20and%20that%20some%20even%20put%20out%20a%20social%20media%20call%20among%20their%20colleagues%20for%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWeibo%20is%20not%20buying%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20people%20on%20Weibo%2C%20China's%20version%20of%20Twitter%2C%20were%20unconvinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20users%20began%20questioning%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20donations%20after%20Yu%20released%20a%20video%20on%20Douyin%2C%20China's%20version%20of%20TikTok%2C%20sharing%20the%20events%20that%20occurred.%20Her%20video%20has%20also%20been%20taken%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20she%20posted%20several%20screenshots%20of%20texts%20with%20her%20husband%20discussing%20the%20organization%20of%20the%20blood%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20Ngari%20region's%20type%20A%20blood%20has%20been%20transfused%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Yu's%20husband%20wrote%20in%20the%20screenshot%2C%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BA%20total%20of%20more%20than%207%2C000%20milliliters%2C%20your%20entire%20body's%20worth%20of%20blood%20was%20replaced%20twice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYu%20thus%20went%20viral%20in%20late%20November%20under%20the%20moniker%20%26quot%3BBlood%20Tank%20Sister%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BHealth%20Bar%20Sister%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reference%20to%20health%20points%20or%20hit%20points%20from%20video%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20conspiracy%20theory%20%E2%80%94%20which%20remains%20unsupported%20by%20any%20confirmed%20evidence%20%E2%80%94%20began%20to%20form%20online%20about%20Yu.%20It%20alleged%20that%20her%20relative%20may%20have%20held%20a%20position%20of%20influence%20and%20compelled%20the%20Shanghai%20Municipal%20Health%20Commission%20to%20force%20Tibetan%20civil%20servants%20into%20donating%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20similar%20situation%20occurs%20again%2C%20could%20you%20replicate%20the%20same%20process%3F%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F7516679696%2FNvTosc6uQ%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20person%20wrote%20on%20Weibo.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20passing%20the%20civil%20service%20exam%2C%20all%20that%20you%20are%20is%20a%20mobile%20blood%20bank%20for%20the%20rich%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EControversy%20brewed%20further%20when%20Yu's%20family%20said%20she%20was%20flown%20from%20Tibet%20to%20Sichuan%20province%20on%20October%2018%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F1420157965%2FNuPhCbXO2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evia%20a%20chartered%20Gulfstream%20G550%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20cost%20over%20%24160%2C000%20to%20hire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20unproven%2C%20the%20conspiracy%20theory's%20infamy%20underscores%20concerns%20in%20China%20of%20corruption%20within%20the%20country's%20healthcare%20system%20and%20the%20treatment%20of%20its%20minority%20ethnic%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tibetan%20minority%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20drew%20national%20attention%20in%202008%20following%20a%20series%20of%20demonstrations%20and%20violent%20encounters%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2F60-years-after-dalai-lama-fled-china-defends-tibet-policies-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETibetans%20protesting%20their%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224312%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20obtained%20on%20March%2022%2C%202008%20shows%20a%20Tibetan%20m)%20running%20past%20burning%20vehicles%2C%20on%20March%2014%2C%202008%20in%20Lhasa%2C%20as%20the%20Tibetan%20capital%20erupted%20in%20deadly%20violence%20with%20security%20forces%20using%20gunfire%20to%20quell%20the%20biggest%20protests%20against%20Chinese%20rule%20in%20two%20decades.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6576a2ee7a3c8094d5db7b97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222868%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhoto%20obtained%20on%20March%2022%2C%202008%20shows%20a%20Tibetan%20m)%20running%20past%20burning%20vehicles%2C%20on%20March%2014%2C%202008%20in%20Lhasa%2C%20as%20the%20Tibetan%20capital%20erupted%20in%20deadly%20violence%20with%20security%20forces%20using%20gunfire%20to%20quell%20the%20biggest%20protests%20against%20Chinese%20rule%20in%20two%20decades.%3Cp%3ERUNE%20BACKS%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EState%20media%20tries%20to%20allay%20controversy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20state%20media%20and%20social%20media%20censors%20have%20since%20moved%20in%20unison%20to%