rvey%20in%20Bihar%20when%20it%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20claimed%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20were%20some%20issues%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20caste-based%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20central%20government%20never%20had%20any%20intention%20of%20creating%20hurdles%20in%20the%20caste-based%20survey.%20When%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power%20in%20Bihar%2C%20it%20supported%20the%20caste-based%20survey.%20The%20governor%20also%20approved%20the%20bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20August%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-govt-defensive-over-bihar-caste-survey-changes-affidavit-in-supreme-court%5C%22%3Ehad%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20noting%2C%20controversially%2C%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20other%20body%20under%20the%20Constitution%20or%20otherwise%20is%20entitled%20to%20conduct%20the%20exercise%20of%20either%20census%20or%20any%20action%20akin%20to%20census.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20it%20changed%20the%20paragraph%20in%20a%20fresh%20affidavit%2C%20claiming%20this%20one%20line%20had%20%E2%80%9Cinadvertently%20crept%20in%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20also%20held%20that%20the%20Census%20Act%20of%201948%20empowers%20only%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20conduct%20the%20Census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20coalition%20of%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20had%20been%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Union%20government%2C%20which%20is%20largely%20understood%20to%20be%20against%20a%20Caste%20Census%20nationally%20at%20this%20point.%20Bihar%20eventually%20finished%20the%20state%20caste%20survey%2C%20and%20tabled%20the%20report%20in%20the%20assembly.%20Similar%20surveys%20are%20being%20conducted%20in%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20comments%20may%20be%20construed%20as%20defensive%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20stance%20that%20it%20is%20the%20sole%20authority%20which%20can%20conduct%20such%20an%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702274140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26170436%2FScreenshot-2023-08-26-at-5.04.26-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Funion-govt-never-intended-to-create-hurdles-in-caste-based-survey-amit-shah%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20home%20minister's%20comments%20may%20be%20construed%20as%20defensive%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20government's%20earlier%20stance%20that%20it%20is%20the%20sole%20authority%20which%20can%20conduct%20such%20an%20exercise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Funion-govt-never-intended-to-create-hurdles-in-caste-based-survey-amit-shah%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stock%20Market%20LIVE%3A%20Sensex%20hits%2070%2C000%2C%20Nifty%20at%2021K%3B%20PSU%20Bank%20stocks%20lead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702272562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-12%2F06%2Ffull%2F1701832563-1791.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-today-nse-bse-sensex-nifty-gift-nifty-mazagon-dock-rec-crude-oil-123121100067_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20Market%20LIVE%20on%20December%2011%2C%202023%3A%20The%20BSE%20Sensex%20crossed%20the%20historic%2070%2C000%20