nimals%20is%20wrong%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20alternative%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20we%20spoke%20was%20in%20February%202020.%20He%20was%20typically%20generous%20with%20his%20time%2C%20turning%20what%20was%20officially%20a%20one-hour%20slot%20into%20a%20two-hour%20discussion%20ranging%20widely%20between%20Extinction%20Rebellion%2C%20the%20Trump%20presidency%2C%20environmental%20tokenism%20and%20the%20need%20for%20Rastafari%20to%20attempt%20amplify%20its%20voice%20in%20ecological%20debates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20still%20now%20recall%20his%20powerful%20and%20vivid%20descriptions%20of%20communing%20with%20the%20nature%20and%20the%20Almighty%20in%20parallel.%20He%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%20when%20I%20meditate%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20question%20about%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20God%20or%20not%2C%20I%20feel%20God.%20And%20at%20the%20same%20time%20I%E2%80%99m%20feeling%20God%20I%20feel%20my%20relationship%20to%20the%20tree%2C%20I%20feel%20my%20relationship%20to%20the%20grass%2C%20I%20feel%20my%20relationship%20to%20the%20animals.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20thing%20I%20feel%20more%20than%20anything%2C%20more%20than%20my%20hand%20more%20than%20my%20foot%2C%20more%20than%20my%20brain.%20That%20feels%20like%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20people%20I%E2%80%99ve%20interviewed%20recognise%20Zephaniah%20as%20a%20figure%20of%20authentic%20and%20artistic%20Rastafari%20spirituality.%20In%20a%20system%20which%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Ftopic%2FRastafari%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cdownpresses%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20movement%2C%20his%20mere%20presence%20served%20to%20demystify%20and%20to%20normalise%20it.%20As%20he%20once%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjzL9A895KJ0%5C%22%3Eput%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seed%20of%20Abraham%20grows%2C%20it%20will%20not%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20those%20who%20see%20it%20know%2C%20Rastafari%20is%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreat%20schools%20and%20churches%20have%20been%20built%20to%20hide%20us%20from%20the%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20that%20built%20burn%20in%20their%20guilt%2C%20as%20prophecies%20reveal.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F219515%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJoseph%20Powell%2C%20British%20Academy%20Postdoctoral%20Research%20Fellow%2C%20Faculty%20of%20Divinity%2C%20University%20of%20Cambridge.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fhow-benjamin-zephaniah-became-the-face-of-british-rastafari-219515%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702270797000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11102841%2FUntitled-design-15-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbenjamin-zephaniah-obituary-british-rastafarian%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Zephaniah%20had%20seemingly%20eternal%20optimism.%20This%20never%20limited%20his%20ability%20to%20confront.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbenjamin-zephaniah-obituary-british-rastafarian%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australia%20to%20halve%20immigration%20intake%2C%20toughen%20English%20test%20for%20students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702270281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_new